metadata.name: Illumination
metadata.description:
This dark image, with the deep valley where the river takes its last breath, and the tunnel that is filled with light, had a strange feeling for myself when their shapes came together. 
For hours, I can stare at this combination with different feelings that take me to the past and future;
Fear
Calmness 
Sorrow
Passion
Anxiety
Silence
Freedom
Dependency
Security
and trembling.
All come to me depending on my mood.
However, I am the one who always spins in the tunnel. 
The light is the point of arrival and the path to it;
A realm of changeable emotions.
